{"tid":92343,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲打算去日本留學？","createTime":"2017-01-23T13:44:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-28T15:37:17.000Z","uid":3818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d027a59dc911df3ed124618019bf83564ae39b5c","tid":92343,"uid":3818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T13:44:29.000Z","msg":"係幾個po留左言都冇人覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想集合一啲有意去日本留學既巴絲一齊傾下<br />\n<br />\n近年考慮到自己都唔細 份工搵得唔多又冇前途又頹 諗下仲有少少青春 打算出去見識下 自己日文都係初學 不過就好有興趣 上網睇完一輪資料 大概以我會考完就出後做野 係要讀一年語言學校先可以考入學試 <br />\n<br />\n我想問下到底語言學校係純教你日文定係其它學術上既野都會教？佢又有分1年同年半等等既課程 日文上到手的話 係咪1年就夠？<br />\n<br />\n銀行要有幾多錢先會批比你留學？<br />\n有啲話廿萬 有啲話幾十萬<br />\n<br />\n諗好讀邊間語言學校係咪自己聯絡果間野就得？搵中介會唔會好啲？<br />\n<br />\n我初步係打算18年4月入學 有冇人一齊傾下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1ddb0d022f0aa75671815ef17115dfeb4a37f41","tid":92343,"uid":1169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T13:48:31.000Z","msg":"exchange算唔算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94d0852d715ffcbf381476e77b13d74a932b9fd2","tid":92343,"uid":3818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T14:08:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>exchange算唔算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"2ee8aa0ae098fbb23b93a0355afaddd69f27ac61","tid":92343,"uid":3818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T14:41:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c8c978e605b4d086db731abf69fee9f672cafd9","tid":92343,"uid":1169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T15:45:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>exchange算唔算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<