","tid":92343,"uid":14797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T17:53:59.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n<br />\n冇錢但想去試下"},{"pid":"98eb605281d032f1e3ca71763ba74c8328b017cd","tid":92343,"uid":3818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T18:22:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黎緊4月去讀語言學校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n關於存款證明要幾多係睇你留學嘅時間長短而唔同<br />\n留學一年嘅話大慨要出示到20萬港元以上存款證明</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我要下年4月先報 儲多少少同埋準備好啲先去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  巴打諗好報邊間未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c6c599fe6f9ed372db0d2934d9852b1fd102e80","tid":92343,"uid":3818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T18:22:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名<br />\n<br />\n冇錢但想去試下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都冇錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  儲落都係十幾萬 要跪下老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c631198a98dc18e6dbb9d9c843bec27f2cf59f8","tid":92343,"uid":3818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T18:25:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>黎緊4月去讀語言學校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n關於存款證明要幾多係睇你留學嘅時間長短而唔同<br />\n留學一年嘅話大慨要出示到20萬港元以上存款證明</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我要下年4月先報 儲多少少同埋準備好啲先去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  巴打諗好報邊間未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲有諗好eju考邊科未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上網睇好似除左選擇題仲會有500字既作文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  應該類似通識？"},{"pid":"7da53dcc1ae2c6dd0267d02b90436135a3b0086c","tid":92343,"uid":11813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T01:49:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>黎緊4月去讀語言學校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n關於存款證明要幾多係睇你留學嘅時間長短而唔同<br />\n留學一年嘅話大慨要出示到20萬港元以上存款證明</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我要下年4月先報 儲多少少同埋準備好啲先去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  巴打諗好報邊間未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲有諗好eju考邊科未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上網睇好似除左選擇題仲會有500字既作文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  應該類似通識？</blockquote><br />\n差唔多半前已經報左語言學校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n基本上語言學校淨係得日文堂<br />\n另外有部份語言學校就有加錢上其他堂 英文 數學等等<br />\n<br />\neju未諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"466535b13181658be07aa28a77fa445db8aec6f2","tid":92343,"uid":72750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T01:55:38.000Z","msg":"去完exchange <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n經u去<br />\n我個時係銀行要有100萬日圓（7萬幾港紙）<br />\n日文程度已經pass左N1不過其他同學pass左N2就可以去<br />\n過到去都係上日文堂同埋上用日文教既堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3c49ca661c01c586019be13ac3da1a445444708","tid":92343,"uid":5313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T07:29:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去完exchange <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n經u去<br />\n我個時係銀行要有100萬日圓（7萬幾港紙）<br />\n日文程度已經pass左N1不過其他同學pass左N2就可以去<br />\n過到去都係上日文堂同埋上用日文教既堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要7萬hkd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57c008a2bb7021811d0369de1bb2189f0dcd2d28","tid":92343,"uid":67302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T07:30:57.000Z","msg":"有無人考慮讀短大？"},{"pid":"eb75ed059706f19e8298a352744e8395af69cf2f","tid":92343,"uid":95584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T15:37:17.000Z","msg":"巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}